{"word":"ἀεργός","slug":"ἀεργός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀεργός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>*<a href='S:ἔργω'><el>ἔργω</el></a>\n<p/><i>not-working, idle</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>;— <el>ἀεργοὶ δόμοι</el> <i>idle</i> houses, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> <i>where people are idle</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b>—<a href='S:confer, compare'>Cf.</a> attic <el>ἀργός.</el><p/>"}]}